      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOTOX CHEVY (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 3 lengths into third (16.24) at this track in a Maiden over 272m. Winning claims. SUPER SKUNK (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only one length (16.10) behind Poppy's Fox at this track. Will give a great sight again. KILCOY PEARL (8) shows ability but remains a maiden after 15 starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing sixth (17.33) at this track. Key runner on best form. PRINCESS ENERGY (7) will be hard to beat with a drop in distance.",
